Grammar

    0 $accept: Program $end

    1 Program: Decls

    2 Decls: Decls Decl
    3      | ε

    4 Decl: FuncDecl
    5     | VarDecl
    6     | TypeDecl

    7 FuncDecl: VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON
    8         | VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES FuncBody

    9 FuncBody: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

   10 VarDecl: VarType VarList SEMICOLON

   11 TypeDecl: _VarType SEMICOLON

   12 VarType: _VarType
   13        | CONST _VarType

   14 _VarType: BuiltinType
   15         | STRUCT IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   16         | UNION IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   17         | ENUM IDENTIFIER LBRACE EnumList RBRACE
   18         | _VarType ASTERISK
   19         | IDENTIFIER

   20 VarList: VarList COMMA VarInit
   21        | VarInit
   22        | ε

   23 VarInit: IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList
   24        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN Expr
   25        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN LBRACE InitList RBRACE
   26        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN LBRACE RBRACE

   27 InitList: InitList COMMA InitItem
   28         | InitItem

   29 InitItem: Expr
   30         | LBRACE InitList RBRACE

   31 ArrayBoundList: ArrayBoundList ArrayBound
   32               | ArrayBound
   33               | ε

   34 ArrayBound: LBRACKET INTEGER RBRACKET
   35           | LBRACKET RBRACKET

   36 ParamList: ParamList COMMA Param
   37          | ParamList COMMA ELLIPSES
   38          | Param
   39          | ELLIPSES
   40          | ε

   41 Param: VarType IDENTIFIER
   42      | VarType

   43 BuiltinType: CHAR
   44            | SHORT
   45            | INT
   46            | LONG
   47            | UNSIGNED
   48            | UNSIGNED CHAR
   49            | UNSIGNED SHORT
   50            | UNSIGNED INT
   51            | UNSIGNED LONG
   52            | FLOAT
   53            | DOUBLE
   54            | BOOL
   55            | VOID

   56 FieldDecls: FieldDecls FieldDecl
   57           | ε

   58 FieldDecl: VarType MemberList SEMICOLON
   59          | SEMICOLON

   60 MemberList: MemberList COMMA IDENTIFIER
   61           | IDENTIFIER
   62           | ε

   63 EnumList: EnumList COMMA Enum
   64         | Enum
   65         | ε

   66 Enum: IDENTIFIER
   67     | IDENTIFIER ASSIGN INTEGER

   68 Stmts: Stmts Stmt
   69      | ε

   70 Stmt: Expr SEMICOLON
   71     | IfStmt
   72     | SwitchStmt
   73     | ForStmt
   74     | DoStmt
   75     | WhileStmt
   76     | ContinueStmt
   77     | BreakStmt
   78     | ReturnStmt
   79     | Block
   80     | TypeDecl
   81     | VarDecl
   82     | SEMICOLON

   83 IfStmt: IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt ELSE Stmt
   84       | IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   85 SwitchStmt: SWITCH LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES LBRACE CaseStmtList RBRACE

   86 CaseStmtList: CaseStmtList CaseStmt
   87             | ε

   88 CaseStmt: CASE Expr COLON Stmts
   89         | DEFAULT COLON Stmts

   90 ForStmt: FOR LPARENTHESES Expr SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   91        | FOR LPARENTHESES SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   92        | FOR LPARENTHESES VarDecl Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   93 DoStmt: DO Stmt WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON

   94 WhileStmt: WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   95 ContinueStmt: CONTINUE SEMICOLON

   96 BreakStmt: BREAK SEMICOLON

   97 ReturnStmt: RETURN SEMICOLON
   98           | RETURN Expr SEMICOLON

   99 Block: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

  100 Expr: IDENTIFIER
  101     | Constant
  102     | LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES
  103     | Expr COMMA Expr
  104     | IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ExprList RPARENTHESES
